data.description:
Stunning Three Bedroom, Two and a Half Bath Ranch Home Available Now! Sitting on approximately Four Acres with a Pond, this Home is Ready to Move In Immediately! Minutes from all that Wooster Has to Offer! Spacious and Updated Interior! Basement is Perfect for Recreation! Barn in the Beautiful Back Yard for Extra Storage! You must see this home to believe it! Tenant Pays All Utilities. Pets Allowed! Schedule your Showing Today!

Rental Insurance Required.

Pets Allowed. A pet is $50 extra per month plus a $200 nonrefundable pet deposit.

Application Fee is NON-Refundable.

**Thorough background checks will be performed for final approval**

Requirements include:
* To hold a property, we need a holding deposit paid by cash or money order.
* Once approved, after the application process is completed & step 1 is done, the following applies for remaining funds due:
If signed before the 20th of the month, deposit given at showing + prorated rent for the rest of the month is due at signing.
If signed after the 20th of the month, deposit given at showing + prorated for the rest of the month and next month rent is all due.

Qualifications include;
Must have the same source of income or same employment for 6+ months at the time of application. Unemployment compensation will not be considered if it is the sole source of income.
6+ months with current employer
500+ beacon credit score
No evictions within the past 5 years
No felonies within the past 5 years
Income must equal 3x the rent rate (co-applicants combined income may be used to meet this qualification) Unverifiable income will not be considered.
